cap emails, the story keeps moving. Loom AI cues 'lights, camera, action' even when you're OOO."},aiSuperstar:{backgroundColor:"#F8EEFE",backgroundStripeColor:"#EED7FC",filmStripTopColor:"#357DE8",filmStripBottomColor:"#1868DB",filmStripBoxColor:"#1868DB",textColor:"#101214",title:"AI Superstar",description:"Your mantra? Work smarter, not harder. Turning videos into emails, chat messages, Jira work items, and more - you let Loom AI do the heavy lifting, so you can focus on the bigger picture. If there was a Walk of Fame star for productivity, your name would be on it."},filmBuff:{backgroundColor:"#E9F2FE",backgroundStripeColor:"#CFE1FD",filmStripTopColor:"#94C748",filmStripBottomColor:"#6A9A23",filmStripBoxColor:"#6A9A23",textColor:"#101214",title:"Film Buff",description:"Press play, sit back, and maybe grab some popcorn. When it comes to Loom, you love nothing more than a front-row seat - just the type of audience every creator wants. You're constantly absorbing information from your team's Looms, always in the know."},director:{backgroundColor:"#1C2B42",backgroundStripeColor:"#123263",filmStripTopColor:"#FFC716",filmStripBottomColor:"#FA8700",filmStripBoxColor:"#FA8700",textColor:"white",title:"Director",description:"You're never shy to call “action” - ready to turn quick updates into blockbuster presentations. As one of Loom's top users, you set the pace for your team. If we had a red carpet, we'd roll it out for you…because every project you touch deserves a premiere."},timeSaver:{backgroundColor:"#FFE48F",backgroundStripeColor:"#FFF5D4",filmStripTopColor:"#357DE8",filmStripBottomColor:"#1558BC",filmStripBoxColor:"#1868DB",textColor:"#101214",title:"Time Saver",description:"You're everyone's favorite teammate, turning Looms into the gift of time. Because why make an update a Shakespeare-worthy monologue, if it can be said in three minutes, watched in any timezone, on 1.5x?"}},M=new Date("2025-12-09"),U=new Date("2026-1-31")},20116:function(e){"use strict";var t,